rComments: Professor Prince is hands-down one of the best professors I've had at uOttawa. She is super caring, extremely passionate about her work and always ready to help out when you need it. Her lectures give you everything you need and she also gives out extra ressources if ever you want to learn more. She has clear grading and feedback!

Professor Prince is a very sweet and accommodating lady. Her essay assignments in this course are a bit formulaic and not really of any practical use, but if you want a consistent and straightforward class with only a handful of assignments, this ones for you. You wont learn a thing but the professor makes this one of the better theatre courses.
teacherRatingTags: ['Gives good feedback', 'Graded by few things', 'Accessible outside class']

rComments: Time for an updated rating! I cannot stress how lovely she is as a professor and a person. She understood that the pandemic was rough on us, so she scraped all tests and the exam and gave us a lot of assignments instead. The assignments were also super easy and straightforward. I recommend her with my whole heart.

If ever there was an epidemic that wiped out all of the theatre profs except for Kathryn Prince & she ended up teaching all of the classes, I would be OK with that. I could listen to her lecture all day, she's always super helpful, and she makes you WANT TO learn. If you're on Rabaska right now thinking about taking a course with her, DO IT!!!

Wonderful prof. Always smiling and happy to help students whenever they need it. Lectures and assignments are clear. Work is relatively simple, but depending on the assignment requires lots of creative thinking/effort. If you put in effort you will do well.
Simply a wonderful teacher and person. Always look forward to her classes. Always willing to go an extra mile to help students, but get ready for some hard work.

she goes to great lengths to make sure students succeed in her classes. Respectable prof. who tries to help her students raise their GPAs if nothing else. I have taken 3 courses with her and it is not enough!

Awesome! She's the best new theatre prof at U Ottawa. Her classes aren't easy, but she gives you what you need to ace them if you want to.  I wish she would teach Theory of the theatrical event this year.
